[[module css]]
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Barlow+Condensed:ital,wght@0,100;0,200;0,300;0,400;0,500;0,600;0,700;0,800;0,900;1,100;1,200;1,300;1,400;1,500;1,600;1,700;1,800;1,900&display=swap');

h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6 {
    color: #000;
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed';
}

::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{
    background: #c3a145;
}
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover{
    background: #846f35;
}
::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
    background: #000;
}

.button{
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 30%;
    margin: auto;
    border: solid 2px white;
    font-size: .95em;
    font-weight: bold;
    text-align: center;
    background-color: black;
    color: white;
    outline: solid 1px white;
    transition: color 0.15s ease-out, background-color 0.05s ease, outline 0.175s ease-out;
    cursor: pointer;
}

.button:is(:hover,:focus) {
    background-color: #c3a145;
    outline-width: .25rem;
}

.button a:link {
    color: #ffffff;
}

.button a:visited {
    color: #ffffff;
}

a:link {
    color: #c3a145;
}


#header {
    height: 240px;
    background-image: url('https://scp-wiki.wikidot.com//local--files/theme:much-cool/logo.png');
    background-position: 50% 20%;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-size: 330px auto;
}
#page-title {
    display: none;
}

.awcyWebHeader {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed';
    background: black;
    text-align:center;
    font-style:italic;
}

.awcyWebHeader p{
    margin: 0;
}

.awcyWebBody {
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed';
    background: black;
    text-align:center;
}

.awcyWebBody p{
    margin: 0 1em 0 1em;
}

.awcySubheader {
    text-align: center;
    color: white;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 2em;
    font-family: 'Barlow Condensed';
    background: #888888;
    padding: 0.5em 1em 0.5em 1em;
}

.awcySubheader p{
    margin-top: 0;
}

.awcySubheader > .button p{
    margin: 0;
}

#page-content > .button a{
    color: white;
}

#page-content img{
    border: gold 1px solid;
}

[[/module]]
[[div class="awcyWebHeader" style="border: red 3px solid;"]]
[[span style="margin: 0;font-family: 'Barlow Condensed'; font-weight: 700; font-size: 5em;color:white;"]] Are We Cool Yet? [[/span]]
[[/div]]
[[div class="awcySubheader"]]
//Are We Cool Yet// is an invitation-only artist collective dedicated to creating the most impactful, thought provoking meaningful works of art that can exist. We use our anomalous gifts to create art that could not exist without us, art that questions the foundational assumptions society works off of, art that will revolutionize the world.
[[/div]]

[[=]]
+ [[span class="h1" style="font-size: 2em;"]] Who Are We? [[/span]]
[[=image 1024px-2016.05.07_Funk_Parade_Washington%2C_DC_USA_04690_%2826615764000%29.jpg style="width: 70%;"]]

+++ We are artists. Independent thinkers. Rebels against the status quo. We see the potential, and we seize it. Morality? Weakness? Boredom? Non-coolness? We reject it all, eschewing the shackles of commercial art, and elevating ourselves into a higher state of being.

+++ We are the Artists and the World is Our Canvas.
[[=image 2008_Gretna_Heritage_Festival_Pink_Art_Woman.jpg style="width: 70%;"]]
[[/=]]
@@ @@
[[div class="awcyWebHeader" style="border: red 3px solid;"]]
[[span style="margin: 0;font-family: 'Barlow Condensed'; font-weight: 700; font-size: 5em;color:white;"]] Join AWCY [[/span]]
[[/div]]
[[div class="awcySubheader"]]
So you want to be part of our collective of artists across the globe, creating revolutionary works of art?  No problem, we'd love to have you in our community!

To join, you must meet the following requirements:
[[div style="background: #d1d1d1; color: black;"]]
[[<]]
* You are currently of consenting age;[[footnote]] In your respective country, dimension, freeport, exoplanetary settlement or otherwise. [[/footnote]]
* You are willing to get a tattoo as a part of your initiation;
* You are currently not, nor have ever been an employee of The Foundation, Foundation subsidiaries, or any other normalcy organizations;
* You create art.
[[/<]]
[[/div]]

If you meet the above qualifications, you can submit your application using the link below! (Please note: There is a mandatory application fee.)
[[div class="button"]]
Join AWCY
[[/div]]
[[/div]]
@@ @@
[[div class="awcyWebHeader" style="border: red 3px solid;"]]
[[span style="margin: 0;font-family: 'Barlow Condensed'; font-weight: 700; font-size: 5em;color:white;"]] Meet The Arts Council [[/span]]
[[/div]]
[[div class="awcySubheader"]]
The //Arts Council// is formed of the top anomalous artists throughout this universe and beyond. We are a trusted group of cultural leaders, influential artists, established patrons and the original founding members of //Are We Cool Yet//, who guide our collective towards greatness.
[[/div]]
[[=]]
[[=image Urban_art_festival_afterPARTY_%2835458792541%29.jpg style="width: 70%;"]]
+++ We are a council of experts, each with our own laundry list of accolades, artworks and insights - together we shape what our collective is, by coordinating events, allocating funds, planning exhibitions and more!

+++ Membership to the Arts Council is offered to members on a case-by-case basis, and happens once per year during the //Induction Ceremony//.

+++ The Arts Council focuses on keeping our artist collective running smoothly, another individual makes the decisions for the direction and mission of //Are We Cool Yet//:
@@ @@
[[/=]]

[[div class="awcyWebHeader" style="border: gold 4px solid; color: white;"]]
[[span style="margin: 0;font-family: 'Barlow Condensed'; font-weight: 700; font-size: 5em;color:white;"]] The Critic [[/span]]
[[/div]]
[[div class="awcyWebHeader"]]
[[=image Queen_of_The_Wild_on_her_throne_%288104158776%29_Crop.jpg style="padding-bottom:0px;"]]
[[span style="margin: 0;font-family: 'Barlow Condensed'; font-weight: 400; font-size: 2em;color:white;"]] Imogen Harper, The Critic (2008-2010) [[/span]]
@@ @@
[[/div]]
[[div class="awcyWebBody" style="color:white;"]]
[[span style="margin: 0;font-family: 'Barlow Condensed'; font-weight: 700; font-size: 3em;color:white; font-style: normal;"]] __So Who Is 'The Critic?'__ [[/span]]
[[span style="margin: 0;font-family: 'Barlow Condensed'; font-weight: 500; font-size: 1.5em;"]] The Critic is an appointed position that determines the overall vision, mission and message of //Are We Cool Yet//. They are chosen on the retirement of the former Critic, selected from who we feel are the most promising up-and-coming artists, revolutionizing the anomalous art world. [[/span]]
@@ @@
[[span style="margin: 0;font-family: 'Barlow Condensed'; font-weight: 500; font-size: 1.5em;"]] Former Critics have been undiscovered maestros, reclusive artistic hermits, Deer College Students, mothers, conceptual beings and more! We are always looking for new potential candidates for the position of Critic, so who knows, YOU might be next... [[/span]]
@@ @@
[[/div]]
